# Project Documentation Walkthrough - KPI_CALC

We have completed the exhaustive documentation of the KPI_CALC Django project. This process involved a deep-dive analysis of every file, culminating in a premium, visual PDF report.

## 1. Project Analysis & Markdown Series
First, the entire codebase was analyzed and a 4-part modular documentation was created to ensure no technical detail was missed.

| Part | Contents |
|---|---|
| [Part 1](file:///c:/Users/hibab/Downloads/KPI_CALC-21-02-26/COMPLETE_DOCUMENTATION_PART1.md) | Core Settings, Models (field-by-field), and Routing. |
| [Part 2](file:///c:/Users/hibab/Downloads/KPI_CALC-21-02-26/COMPLETE_DOCUMENTATION_PART2.md) | Detailed UI/Template analysis (all 12 files) with every button and form field. |
