## 2. Visual KPI Analytics
To make the data readable and professional, 15 high-fidelity charts were generated using Matplotlib. These visualize the core metrics mentioned in the business logic:
- Attendance & Consistency Surveys
- Tickets Completed & Story Point Velocity
- Code Quality (Reopened %, Build Fail %)
- Engagement (Commits, Peer Reviews)

